1
00:00:07,725 --> 00:00:11,711
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

2
00:00:11,712 --> 00:00:15,311
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

3
00:00:15,312 --> 00:00:24,132
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on笙ｪ

4
00:00:24,575 --> 00:00:27,061
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

5
00:00:27,062 --> 00:00:29,211
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

6
00:00:29,212 --> 00:00:32,699
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

7
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:40,324
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

8
00:00:40,325 --> 00:00:42,786
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

9
00:00:42,787 --> 00:00:44,786
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

10
00:00:44,787 --> 00:00:48,449
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

11
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:53,836
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

12
00:00:53,837 --> 00:00:56,457
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

13
00:00:56,637 --> 00:00:58,874
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

14
00:00:58,875 --> 00:00:59,779
=Echoes of Love=

15
00:00:59,780 --> 00:01:01,499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

16
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:03,732
=Episode 10=

17
00:01:04,940 --> 00:01:07,874
You have been investigating
the Shengtang Guild in secret.

18
00:01:07,875 --> 00:01:10,682
Does the Duke know of this?

19
00:01:11,139 --> 00:01:12,260
My affairs

20
00:01:12,859 --> 00:01:14,557
have never required his approval.

21
00:01:22,740 --> 00:01:25,058
The Duchess is skilled in song and dance

22
00:01:25,059 --> 00:01:26,939
and adept at navigating official circles.

23
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,120
In the fifth year of Shaoyuan, she founded
the predecessor of the Shengtang Guild,

24
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,459
the Haitang Guild.

25
00:01:31,779 --> 00:01:35,099
She used the courtesans of the capital
to conduct exchanges of wealth and power.

26
00:01:35,100 --> 00:01:37,579
I have long been aware of this matter.

27
00:01:37,580 --> 00:01:40,258
For the sake of my years
of collegial ties with the Duke,

28
00:01:40,259 --> 00:01:41,858
I went to great lengths

29
00:01:41,859 --> 00:01:43,579
to keep it suppressed.

30
00:01:43,740 --> 00:01:44,860
And now,

31
00:01:45,975 --> 00:01:48,374
you intend to investigate it thoroughly.

32
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:59,058
(The Shengtang Guild
has committed countless wrongs.)

33
00:01:59,059 --> 00:02:01,220
(How could it have
been founded by Mother?)

34
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:03,379
(I do not believe it.)

35
00:02:04,259 --> 00:02:06,500
(But if what Official Gao said is true,)

36
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:09,379
(how am I supposed to face Song Zhiyun?)

37
00:02:09,737 --> 00:02:11,749
(Am I to tell her)

38
00:02:12,580 --> 00:02:14,900
(that my mother was the one
who started it all?)

39
00:02:26,099 --> 00:02:27,220
Are you all right?

40
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:29,220
Did Shanguan Yu hurt you?

41
00:02:30,775 --> 00:02:32,214
So Official Gu

42
00:02:32,215 --> 00:02:33,845
cares for me this much.

43
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:35,500
What did you say?

44
00:02:37,539 --> 00:02:39,098
The weather today

45
00:02:39,099 --> 00:02:40,460
is bitterly cold.

46
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:43,080
When I look back,

47
00:02:43,339 --> 00:02:44,500
every step

48
00:02:44,525 --> 00:02:47,283
feels as though
it was carefully arranged.

49
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:49,819
Like a piece upon a chessboard.

50
00:02:50,012 --> 00:02:51,772
I cannot help but wonder

51
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:53,899
whether the truth I seek

52
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:56,020
is meant to punish the true culprit,

53
00:02:56,260 --> 00:02:57,098
or whether I am merely

54
00:02:57,099 --> 00:02:59,500
paving the way for someone
else's ambition and secrets.

55
00:03:02,437 --> 00:03:03,557
Official Gu,

56
00:03:04,659 --> 00:03:06,500
could you clear up a doubt for me?

57
00:03:12,375 --> 00:03:14,425
I watched a play today.

58
00:03:14,659 --> 00:03:15,979
It was about

59
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:19,007
a thief crying thief while stealing
under the guise of oversight.

60
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:21,060
It told of an official

61
00:03:21,539 --> 00:03:23,900
who appeared upright and impartial,

62
00:03:24,099 --> 00:03:26,659
yet secretly colluded with criminals.

63
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:27,979
When matters were exposed,

64
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:30,580
he used his authority to gather evidence
and conceal the truth.

65
00:03:31,580 --> 00:03:32,659
Official Gu,

66
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:34,579
does this story

67
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:36,460
sound familiar to you?

68
00:03:40,539 --> 00:03:42,300
Today I will ask only one thing.

69
00:03:43,099 --> 00:03:45,180
Do you still remember
your original intention?

70
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:47,180
Of all that passed between us,

71
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:49,139
which words were spoken from the heart,

72
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:52,180
and which were merely
convenient tactics?

73
00:03:52,339 --> 00:03:53,179
Song Zhiyun.

74
00:03:53,180 --> 00:03:54,379
Official Gu,

75
00:03:57,379 --> 00:03:58,259
from beginning to end,

76
00:03:58,260 --> 00:03:59,579
were you not using me,

77
00:03:59,580 --> 00:04:01,300
treating me as your blade?

78
00:04:02,099 --> 00:04:03,179
Everything today,

79
00:04:03,180 --> 00:04:04,774
was it not arranged by you?

80
00:04:04,775 --> 00:04:10,295
笙ｪSo many chapters,
every wound remembered笙ｪ

81
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:14,157
笙ｪBack where we once stood,
the blossoms still remain笙ｪ

82
00:04:14,180 --> 00:04:15,300
Yes.

83
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:16,874
I did once say

84
00:04:16,875 --> 00:04:17,949
that you were my blade.

85
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:19,786
笙ｪWave after wave of sorrow笙ｪ

86
00:04:19,787 --> 00:04:21,161
笙ｪIn exchange, no one will ever know笙ｪ

87
00:04:21,162 --> 00:04:22,562
From this day forward,

88
00:04:23,025 --> 00:04:24,770
your mission is complete.

89
00:04:25,299 --> 00:04:26,738
From now on, whatever happens

90
00:04:26,739 --> 00:04:28,380
will have nothing to do with you.

91
00:04:28,859 --> 00:04:29,979
At dawn tomorrow,

92
00:04:30,512 --> 00:04:31,949
I will have someone escort you away.

93
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:35,295
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

94
00:04:36,339 --> 00:04:37,460
Yes.

95
00:04:38,779 --> 00:04:40,619
I overestimated myself,

96
00:04:40,900 --> 00:04:42,619
thinking we were allies.

97
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:44,374
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

98
00:04:44,375 --> 00:04:45,899
From beginning to end,

99
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:47,259
I was nothing more than your pawn.

100
00:04:47,387 --> 00:04:50,338
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

101
00:04:50,339 --> 00:04:51,859
Two people who do not trust each other

102
00:04:52,075 --> 00:04:53,794
should never have joined forces

103
00:04:55,637 --> 00:04:56,796
in the first place.

104
00:04:59,175 --> 00:05:01,282
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

105
00:05:04,099 --> 00:05:06,099
Thank you, Official Gu,
for saving my life.

106
00:05:06,539 --> 00:05:07,745
From this day on,

107
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,340
whether I live or die

108
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,839
will no longer concern you.

109
00:05:18,612 --> 00:05:22,436
笙ｪYou gave me a silent dream笙ｪ

110
00:05:22,437 --> 00:05:26,636
笙ｪTime rushed by,
yet the memories linger long笙ｪ

111
00:05:26,637 --> 00:05:29,949
笙ｪCarrying the weight of hatred笙ｪ

112
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:34,045
笙ｪBurying every trace of love笙ｪ

113
00:05:34,362 --> 00:05:38,348
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

114
00:05:38,349 --> 00:05:41,948
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

115
00:05:41,949 --> 00:05:50,769
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on笙ｪ

116
00:05:51,212 --> 00:05:53,698
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

117
00:05:53,699 --> 00:05:55,848
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

118
00:05:55,849 --> 00:05:59,336
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

119
00:05:59,337 --> 00:06:06,961
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

120
00:06:06,962 --> 00:06:09,423
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

121
00:06:09,424 --> 00:06:11,423
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

122
00:06:11,424 --> 00:06:15,086
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

123
00:06:15,087 --> 00:06:20,473
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

124
00:06:20,474 --> 00:06:23,094
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

125
00:06:25,187 --> 00:06:27,945
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

126
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:32,539
Now that you know the truth,

127
00:06:34,380 --> 00:06:36,419
this matter ends here.

128
00:06:41,339 --> 00:06:43,700
This snow has fallen long enough.

129
00:06:44,700 --> 00:06:46,820
It is time for it to stop.

130
00:06:48,339 --> 00:06:50,220
This world has never been fair.

131
00:06:50,820 --> 00:06:53,539
If I know I am being deceived and used,

132
00:06:53,900 --> 00:06:55,820
yet still refuse to fight for myself,

133
00:06:56,179 --> 00:06:57,580
then one day

134
00:06:57,620 --> 00:06:59,539
I may be devoured
without even a bone left behind.

135
00:07:01,099 --> 00:07:02,739
What else are you trying to do?

136
00:07:02,779 --> 00:07:04,178
Since we have entered a dead end,

137
00:07:04,179 --> 00:07:05,780
we should tear down the wall.

138
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:09,859
Right now, I cannot move a step alone.

139
00:07:09,940 --> 00:07:11,940
Only by joining hands
do we stand a chance.

140
00:07:11,979 --> 00:07:13,579
We will uncover the truth together,

141
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:14,859
and take revenge together,

142
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:17,020
so that every wrongdoer
is brought to justice.

143
00:07:18,779 --> 00:07:20,059
When that day comes,

144
00:07:20,779 --> 00:07:22,020
this snow

145
00:07:23,179 --> 00:07:24,859
will truly have stopped.

146
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:26,460
To investigate this case,

147
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:30,140
we must make use of Gu Chengye.

148
00:07:30,339 --> 00:07:32,780
Since his mother
founded the Shengtang Guild,

149
00:07:32,979 --> 00:07:34,619
we begin with him.

150
00:07:34,700 --> 00:07:36,820
Perhaps we can find crucial evidence

151
00:07:36,859 --> 00:07:38,338
and wipe out the Shengtang Guild

152
00:07:38,339 --> 00:07:39,580
in one stroke.

153
00:07:45,979 --> 00:07:47,380
I will approach him.

154
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:49,979
Since he chose me as his blade,

155
00:07:50,112 --> 00:07:51,552
he should know

156
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,179
that this blade

157
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:55,589
may one day turn against him.

158
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:05,101
This time,

159
00:08:05,219 --> 00:08:06,859
I will be

160
00:08:08,179 --> 00:08:09,482
the one who wields it.

161
00:08:15,419 --> 00:08:16,299
Sir,

162
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:19,619
your subordinate has led men
to search the entire city of Lin'an,

163
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:21,098
yet we have found

164
00:08:21,099 --> 00:08:22,460
no trace of Song Zhiyun.

165
00:08:22,739 --> 00:08:24,460
How interesting.

166
00:08:25,179 --> 00:08:28,140
The one who came and went freely
at Huanyue House that day

167
00:08:28,179 --> 00:08:31,059
has now vanished without a trace.

168
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:35,298
Within this capital,

169
00:08:35,299 --> 00:08:37,660
there is no one I cannot find,

170
00:08:38,779 --> 00:08:40,139
unless

171
00:08:40,459 --> 00:08:43,660
she has already turned to dust,

172
00:08:44,825 --> 00:08:45,985
or

173
00:08:46,125 --> 00:08:48,805
she has been hidden away

174
00:08:49,659 --> 00:08:51,940
by someone with an agenda.

175
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:58,520
(Gu Residence)

176
00:09:18,779 --> 00:09:20,060
Song Zhiyun,

177
00:09:20,980 --> 00:09:22,379
what are you planning now?

178
00:09:23,699 --> 00:09:24,899
Official Gu,

179
00:09:25,699 --> 00:09:27,379
do you truly not feel

180
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:29,899
even the slightest affection for me?

181
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:33,739
Why not

182
00:09:33,939 --> 00:09:35,499
ask right here?

183
00:09:35,812 --> 00:09:37,132
Your heart

184
00:09:37,620 --> 00:09:39,259
does not lie.

185
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:20,178
Official,

186
00:10:20,179 --> 00:10:22,499
how shall we handle
the birthday gifts received today?

187
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:24,099
As usual,

188
00:10:24,579 --> 00:10:26,540
donate them all in full.

189
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:34,619
By the way...

190
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:37,899
Rest assured, we have dispatched
covert guards to protect Miss Song in secret.

191
00:10:38,179 --> 00:10:39,379
However,

192
00:10:39,380 --> 00:10:40,940
there is still no news.

193
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:14,300
Official Gu.

194
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:15,619
Song Zhiyun?

195
00:11:16,699 --> 00:11:17,658
Why are you here?

196
00:11:17,659 --> 00:11:20,460
Shh. I finally
persuaded Wei Cheng to let me in.

197
00:11:21,179 --> 00:11:22,538
Today is your birthday.

198
00:11:22,539 --> 00:11:24,060
How could I not come?

199
00:11:26,260 --> 00:11:27,139
I heard that tonight

200
00:11:27,140 --> 00:11:28,859
there will be
a lantern procession in the city.

201
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:30,219
Why not

202
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:31,700
go and see it together?

203
00:11:34,175 --> 00:11:35,454
Come on.
